videos.headline: Hooker finds the end zone from 12 yards out
videos.description: Virginia Tech quarterback Hendon Hooker scrambles up the middle for a 12-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hooker finds the end zone from 12 yards out) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Hooker takes a hit but finds Keene for the TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Hendon Hooker is able to find Dalton Keene for the touchdown despite the big hit he takes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hooker takes a hit but finds Keene for the TD) 2019/10/05

videos.headline: Miami gets on the board to end the first half
videos.description: Miami gets a touchdown right at the end of the first half when Mark Pope hauls in a deflection for a 38-yard score.

videos.headline: 67-yard pass sets up TD for Hokies
videos.description: Hendon Hooker goes deep to James Mitchell and on the next play Dalton Keene catches a five-yard touchdown.
